('hjres58-115','hjres','Providing for congressional disapproval under chapter 8 of title 5, United States Code, of the rule submitted by the Department of Education relating to teacher preparation issues.','None','None','PASSED:BILL','2017-02-01','(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)

