('hr988-115','hr','To provide for a study by the Transportation Research Board of the National Academies on the impact of diverting certain freight rail traffic to avoid urban areas, and for other purposes.','None','None','REFERRED','2017-02-09','This bill directs the Department of Transportation to make appropriate arrangements with the Transportation Research Board of the National Academies to study the cost and impact of rerouting freight rail traffic of hazardous material to avoid its transportation through urban areas.','115','988'),
('hr989-115','hr','To exempt certain Department of Defense civilian positions from any furlough as a result of a lapse in discretionary appropriations, and for other purposes.','None','None','REFERRED','2017-02-09','This bill exempts Department of Defense (DOD) civilian positions with salaries paid out of a working-capital fund from any furlough order issued as a result of a lapse in discretionary appropriations for DOD.','115','989'),
('hr99-115','hr','To amend the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to provide for the eligibility of Transportation Security Administration employees to receive public safety officers\' death benefits, and for other purposes.','None','Honoring Our Fallen TSA Officers Act','REFERRED','2017-01-03','Honoring Our Fallen TSA Officers Act

