('hres35-115','hres','Expressing the sense of the House of Representatives relating to automated external defibrillator (AED) training in the Nation\'s schools.','None','None','REFERRED','2017-01-09','Encourages public schools with automated external defibrillators (AEDs), during time allocated under state law for training personnel in emergency first aid and CPR (cardiopulmonary resuscitation), to train personnel in the use of AEDs.','115','35'),
