Elects specified Members to the House Committee on Ethics.','115','56'),
('hres57-115','hres','Supporting the contributions of Catholic schools.','None','None','REFERRED','2017-01-24','Expresses support for: (1) the goals of Catholic Schools Week, an event cosponsored by the National Catholic Educational Association and the United States Conference of Catholic Bishops and established to recognize the contributions of Catholic elementary and secondary schools in the United States; and (2) the continued dedication of Catholic schools, students, parents, and teachers toward academic excellence and the key role they play in promoting and ensuring a brighter, stronger future for the nation.','115','57'),
