('hres94-115','hres','Commending Sally Quillian Yates for refusing to enforce Donald Trump\'s discriminatory Executive Order 13769 (82 Fed. Reg. 8977; relating to "Protecting the Nation From Foreign Terrorist Entry Into the United States").','None','None','REFERRED','2017-02-06','Commends Sally Yates for refusing to enforce Executive Order 13769. Among the order\'s major provisions are restrictions on the entry of immigrants and nonimmigrants from seven countries (Iran, Iraq, Libya, Somalia, Sudan, Syria, and Yemen) and additional limitations on refugee admissions to the United States.

