('s67-115','s','A bill to direct the Secretary of State to submit to Congress a report on the designation of Iran\'s Revolutionary Guard Corps as a foreign terrorist organization, and for other purposes.','None','IRGC Terrorist Designation Act','REFERRED','2017-01-09','IRGC Terrorist Designation Act

