('sres45-115','sres','A resolution designating February 2017 as "American Heart Month" and February 3, 2017, as "National Wear Red Day".','None','None','PASSED:SIMPLERES','2017-02-03','(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)

